		<li><strong>Vague specifications:</strong> "Standard materials" without details</li>
		<li><strong>No written contract:</strong> Always get everything in writing</li>
		<li><strong>Pressure tactics:</strong> "This price is only good today" is a red flag</li>
		<li><strong>No license/insurance:</strong> Verify credentials independently</li>
	</ul>

